    task aud_axiom_mark_decoration "Per-participant axiom-mark decoration" {
      effort 1d
      allocate team
      complete 100
      depends !aud_cytoscape_init
      note -8<-
        Refinement: tasks/refinements/audience/aud_axiom_mark_decoration.md

        Per-participant chromatic axiom-mark badges rendered as a DOM-overlay sibling of the
