        Anonymous visitor hits a private session; server rejects the WS subscribe with
        'forbidden'; the graph route currently renders an empty canvas with no user-facing
        message. This task registers a subscribe-rejection-aware sign-in CTA contextualised
        to the session.
        Source: tasks/refinements/audience/aud_session_url.md Open question §1 + Status block.
      ->8-
    }
